ygData.messageBody:
First -

I need to know some good ways to raise faction with Kelethin Merchants - I
know of giving slaves to keys and completing the Banded Orc Vest with
merchant Linadian, are there others? i have a quest that requires me to kill
something that gives bad faction with them, :)

Second -

Does anyone know of anything about a weapon called the "Kilij" ? I am on
the quest, and i am looking for 'the plans for the kilij'
That's what it's called, it's the plans on how the kilij is made, so i can
take them to the guy who can make them, Any info or anyone selling such an
item on Cazic Thule would be welcomed.

Rebequa
18th Rogue
CT
